{"id":"32a35a8ba48c1e895ebb92db4c4952e80a134c25b698f1493ed7a9747b8b48dd","item_id":"5c6f757665:0","text":"有关支持的 Houdini 版本，请访问"}
{"id":"cc74c091bfef2c3f41d2960930716e1f3487a7747c4a16793b13818f31a78645","item_id":"5c6f757665:1","text":"Installation and Licensing（安装与许可）"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"5c6f757665:2","text":"。"}
{"id":"0c65975f71ad276fda57986b58a85ca8c3babfef21111bf4b675284424ff39f7","item_id":"5c6f757665:3","text":"可以使用 RenderMan Installer 安装 RenderMan for Houdini；该安装器负责下载、安装和许可 RenderMan Pro Server（实际渲染器）以及所有桥接产品。"}
{"id":"021a9984ec8cb5c9af0a1c84978c0f21e15b2394f3f9d93aa88d2d76d3658c0e","item_id":"5c6f757665:4","text":"Package Installation（包安装）"}
{"id":"a0770f9bb8d2790576ed499cf6b0242d3e0b89b303dd365cab1e32a794bc8735","item_id":"5c6f757665:5","text":"RenderMan for Houdini 可以通过 packages 文件安装，该文件位于 RfH 安装目录中。"}
{"id":"4c7f649fb11854bc3c9793958a7aef9728ce8a2a22b62b0be51f73f9a4e24f83","item_id":"5c6f757665:6","text":"将 packages JSON 文件复制到下列位置之一，以便 Houdini 在启动时找到它。SideFX 的高级 package 说明在"}
{"id":"fcec91509759ad995c2cd14bcb26b2720993faf61c29d379b270d442d92290eb","item_id":"5c6f757665:7","text":"此处"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"5c6f757665:8","text":"。"}
{"id":"f7611f8897254f496b2ee45fa3d73d04e85a71f6bcf5c5092237dfd949628b75","item_id":"5c6f757665:9","text":"(例如，"}
{"id":"857f9bbeb1e26630dd4a5b7782b9cef3e4ed2a18ec8f6cfa448ca68756bdda54","item_id":"5c6f757665:10","text":"Manual Installation（手动安装）"}
{"id":"ce78506ceb0d5976f0bdc44e95e08c6e39869a96d1f48df7aa79b7a1734dc56f","item_id":"5c6f757665:11","text":"RfH 的环境变量必须在 houdini.env 文件中排在第一位。（Windows 需要使用分号）例如："}
{"id":"de584831a8773dd33af964cc02af01148eb4cad740cb1e5f6699328fe46c51b1","item_id":"5c6f757665:12","text":"HOUDINI_PATH=$RFHTREE/3.11/21.0.512:&"}
{"id":"534f9b13d8f8d52af95c63c3297a8266f925b73f5f44628d408c4a7de8ec9a1b","item_id":"5c6f757665:13","text":"带 Solaris 的 RenderMan for Houdini 需要在配置文件中增加一行，才能渲染内存中的 VDB："}
{"id":"560edef6a2aff6d8c2b8001ac8171f97a95ed6cc5b1401a5bbc5eff738ce9010","item_id":"5c6f757665:14","text":"RMAN_PROCEDURALPATH = $RFHTREE/3.11/21.0.512/openvdb:&"}
{"id":"ba794b220a6c5f96483f04de6e915f857d0624d54af5bd2bdc2f0c4f0451c488","item_id":"5c6f757665:15","text":"从 Houdini 21 开始，为了支持在 RenderMan 中读取 COP 纹理，需要定义以下变量："}
{"id":"864a14f427d7f7c0a1ac05db3c6cc95b2625977caec0004500ec6121fd42712a","item_id":"5c6f757665:16","text":"RMAN_TEXTUREPATH = $RFHTREE/3.11/21.0.512/rtxplugins:&"}
{"id":"448739ea4f4bbdf56197d3663bc4173d4534d62a5c7f6dfe4a651c59bc4436d9","item_id":"5c6f757665:17","text":"RenderMan for Houdini 在"}
{"id":"d598026a9cbc60505f138ce53ac78088d582100c196d0f70c7e2538d4a8d7e10","item_id":"5c6f757665:18","text":"Windows"}
{"id":"3eb07e605a2b63e72a4e11a8cb8c638f57c58e113faa4d4efff5e1a57bfa84f0","item_id":"5c6f757665:19","text":"上需要在配置文件中增加一行："}
{"id":"b093770cd6d623cadb7ce78cce8da3abfe2ce374ffe13def15fc5d8becc6e5fb","item_id":"5c6f757665:20","text":"PATH=$RMANTREE\\bin;&"}
{"id":"50af18201ea76b1706b6d6796cbe465d4aed845c63839ee2938e3f75e401ecd5","item_id":"5c6f757665:21","text":"本文档下方提供了更多说明和详细信息。"}
{"id":"72bce1a18ad5e3871c74510b667c7547df6e7c0eae2e9affd1f63557e5b94277","item_id":"5c6f757665:22","text":"安装插件后，Houdini 需要修改主目录中的 Houdini 环境才能加载 RenderMan 插件。Houdini 专用环境变量也可以在 houdini.env 中设置；各操作系统对应位置如下："}
{"id":"1c298bcd53ada50f2c09be24d86071ddb4d57193de3f062241fc7165c0e40915","item_id":"5c6f757665:23","text":"NOTE（注意）："}
{"id":"5e76efa8c7242d28b67448c1019a92e261758d4a1a4cc3707c180ad75232aadd","item_id":"5c6f757665:24","text":"首次运行新版 Houdini 时，可能需要运行两次，上述位置才会出现 houdini.env 文件；文件创建后，就可以添加下面提到的各行。"}
{"id":"74d032043c6ef3e171f154b64f0153677e88802587f738fbf482d8aefb8dc3b0","item_id":"5c6f757665:25","text":"需要用文本编辑器编辑 houdini.env 文件，并在启动 Houdini 之前把下面几行放入该文件。每个正在使用的 Houdini 新主版本只需要执行一次。"}
{"id":"04a81e6b4883fbf2553a5e9baf9a84b4502b1c1f67eedc4fb20e8f2458b663d4","item_id":"5c6f757665:26","text":"EXAMPLES（示例）"}
{"id":"4f9313e46248b6dffb2f0391d119ebbbf7cd1c680c41f37074573027afe5b9b3","item_id":"5c6f757665:27","text":"例如在 Linux 上，应编辑此文件：$HOME/houdini21.0/houdini.env："}
{"id":"4731ae02f7ed8b8b17d611ae4a7dc9fdf6eaacc8be44dc3edad783f15937300b","item_id":"5c6f757665:28","text":"在 Windows 上，应编辑此文件：\\Users\\"}
{"id":"e06e309b66b35433fd311e9bab12a9843671de60cb122636d43ebd87754ded62","item_id":"5c6f757665:29","text":"myself"}
{"id":"d5e0a6cb136d4a6c800227ef5c6187271e44391d79449238de38b4f1c9aa09e8","item_id":"5c6f757665:30","text":"\\Documents\\houdini21.0\\houdini.env："}
{"id":"7a552636e3317c1d116f1c562c91b3ecff5ffcbb4dc5d1b6b77af7a2b9bef711","item_id":"5c6f757665:31","text":"NOTE（注意）"}
{"id":"8a36c0ef8c6491d581faec652a0ab79b7857853cc1dae3bf7b761345b3e479d7","item_id":"5c6f757665:32","text":"：Windows 使用分号而不是冒号来分隔 HOUDINI_PATH！"}
{"id":"0323b6b069a383cde11bdf4580a434e88613d3cd078fdaaee45580c162cf7dcc","item_id":"5c6f757665:33","text":"最后一个 macOS 示例，应编辑：/Users/"}
{"id":"e06e309b66b35433fd311e9bab12a9843671de60cb122636d43ebd87754ded62","item_id":"5c6f757665:34","text":"myself"}
{"id":"dbfcb25b4ded049dbd54aa390bbbd1b451de03493a09a7ecc06797c9ef4fccaa","item_id":"5c6f757665:35","text":"/Library/Preferences/houdini/21.0/houdini.env："}
